#ad We’re huge fans of family fun and jokes in the East house, and today my friends at @LaffyTaffy helped me play the
ultimate dad joke on @shawnjohnson. 

To celebrate the launch of Laffy Taffy’s Minions LAFF BITES "GONE BANANAS!” I staked our yard with a banana joke to give Shawn some big laffs.... and she thought it was awesome and hilarious.

If you know someone who could use a good laff, you can help Laffy Taffy share sweet joy this summer. Head over to the link in my bio to learn about how you can pass the laff (Terms & Conditions apply). You can also laff along with me by checking
out my joke on IGTV. @CardMyYard #LaffyTaffy #Jokes #DadJokes
